Follow-up implemented in this session:

  We implemented the fail-closed validation gate first.

  Runtime now validates the produced replay report when
  validation_rollout=true. It rejects validation replay if:

    replay report is missing or empty
    completed_count <= 0
    execution_profile_digest is missing
    policy_set_digest is missing
    cajtucu_synthetic_market_step_count > 0
    cajtucu_invalid_trace_count > 0

